{"tid":1654501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[不割席] 我哋仲係度畀中共打到嘔血！","createTime":"2019-10-14T15:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T15:35:46.000Z","uid":283140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d4a3603c56ef01afb10bc3f5b92f62ddd3b57297","tid":1654501,"uid":283140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:35:46.000Z","msg":"做到咩都好，總之不割席！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做得唔好就改善，千祈唔好手足互屌。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">巴絲爬山，各自努力！</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n每一人出一分力，互相扶持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家啲黑警又有伸縮警棍，再加埋胡椒噴霧，無端白事又可以拎支槍出嚟，唔好淨係見到自己人嘅武力，而見唔到對方嘅暴力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪撚企喺度德高地，不食人間煙火。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非你係仆街林鄭，或者一啲用patpat諗嘢嘅建制派，咁你咪可以咁樣做囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}